    <item>
      <title>特朗普能让美国例外主义持续下去吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-12-05/us-stocks-can-trump-make-american-exceptionalism-last</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去 15 年来，美国股市一直领先于其他所有股市。但风险是众所周知的，而且越来越多的人认为这种情况必须继续下去，这让人感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-12-05/us-stocks-can-trump-make-american-exceptionalism-last</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 05:54:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国反对党领袖李龙海支持恢复卖空交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/s-korea-opposition-leader-lee-backs-short-selling-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国反对党领袖李在明是继韩国短暂实施戒严令后接替现任总统的热门人选之一，他赞成恢复股票卖空交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/s-korea-opposition-leader-lee-backs-short-selling-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 05:54:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国迅速应对危机，限制了市场动荡的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/swift-crisis-response-by-korea-limits-market-impact-of-tumult</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国本周短暂实施戒严令，令市场感到恐慌，但官员们迅速采取行动恢复民主规范并安抚投资者，限制了损失——至少目前如此。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/swift-crisis-response-by-korea-limits-market-impact-of-tumult</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 05:44:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>饮料制造商东鹏饮料考虑在香港上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/drink-maker-eastroc-beverage-is-said-to-weigh-hong-kong-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国能量饮料制造商东鹏饮料集团股份有限公司正考虑在香港上市，此前该公司在瑞士发行股票的计划未能实现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/drink-maker-eastroc-beverage-is-said-to-weigh-hong-kong-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 05:28:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗银行如何在澳大利亚大规模大宗交易中损失 1700 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/how-citi-lost-17-million-on-biggest-aussie-block-trade-in-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团本周以低于竞争对手的价格赢得了澳大利亚七年来最大的大宗交易，但交易最终却以失败告终，导致这家美国银行的账面上有大量未售出的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/how-citi-lost-17-million-on-biggest-aussie-block-trade-in-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 03:39:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年印尼最大规模 IPO 后，Adaro Andalan 股价上涨 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/adaro-andalan-rises-20-in-indonesia-s-largest-ipo-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[煤炭开采商 PT Adaro Andalan Indonesia 的股价在首个交易日上涨，显示出市场对印尼一年半以来最大规模首次公开募股 (IPO) 的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/adaro-andalan-rises-20-in-indonesia-s-largest-ipo-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 02:28:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命 SEC 官员支持加密货币，比特币价格突破 10 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/bitcoin-btc-nears-record-100-000-on-trump-s-pick-of-atkins-for-sec</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国候任总统唐纳德·特朗普选择一位加密货币支持者担任下一任美国证券监管机构负责人，此举使比特币价格首次升至 10 万美元，交易员们对放松监管的前景感到乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/bitcoin-btc-nears-record-100-000-on-trump-s-pick-of-atkins-for-sec</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 01:17:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 供应决策备受关注，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在下跌后企稳，交易员们期待周四举行的 OPEC+ 会议，预计该组织将再次推迟在供应已经充足的市场中恢复产量的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 23:34:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市波动；比特币突破 100,000 美元：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市窄幅波动，该地区货币保持相对平静，因为交易员正在消化法国和韩国政治风暴的影响。比特币突破 100,000 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 22:39:22 GMT</pubDate>
